outputs.output_descr: The project is designed to serve as an instrument for national capacity development, specifically to enable ETO discharge its mandated roles and contribute to the attainment of tourism sector goals set in the Growth and Transformational Plan (GTP). The project strengthens technical and policy advisory capacity of Ethiopian Tourism Organization (ETO)  as well as  facilitates the creation, acquisition, and use of proven knowledge and technologies in tourism development.

project_descr: The Project  strengthens technical and policy advisory capacity of Ethiopian Tourism Organization (ETO) as well as to facilitates  creation, acquisition, and use of proven knowledge and technologies in tourism development.
project_title: Capacity Strengthening for Ethiopian Tourism Org.
